---
// Hero section — full viewport, typography-only manifesto opening
---

<section id="manifesto" class="relative min-h-[100dvh] flex items-center justify-center px-6">
  <!-- Red vertical bar -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-1/4 bottom-1/4 w-1.5 bg-brand-red"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h1 class="font-display font-black text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-tight tracking-tight uppercase">
      Todo projeto<br />
      <span class="text-brand-red">tem um propósito.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-8 font-display font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-black/60 tracking-wide">
      A gente constrói universos. E conhece cada pessoa que entra neles.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-pulse-down">
    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-brand-black/40">
      <path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
